quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  2,1,’Alif lām mīm
  2,2,"Èyí ni Tírà náà, tí kò sí iyèméjì nínú rẹ̀. Ìmọ̀nà ni fún àwọn olùbẹ̀rù (Allāhu)"
  2,3,"àwọn t’ó gbàgbọ́ nínú (ìró) ìkọ̀kọ̀, tí wọ́n ń kírun, tí wọ́n sì ń ná nínú ohun tí A pèsè fún wọn"
  2,4,"àti àwọn t’ó gbàgbọ́ nínú ohun tí A sọ̀kalẹ̀ fún ọ àti ohun tí A sọ̀kalẹ̀ ṣíwájú rẹ, tí wọ́n sì ní àmọ̀dájú nípa Ọjọ́ Ìkẹ́yìn"
  2,5,"Àwọn wọ̀nyẹn wà lórí ìmọ̀nà láti ọ̀dọ̀ Olúwa wọn. Àwọn wọ̀nyẹn, àwọn ni olùjèrè"
  2,6,"Dájúdájú àwọn t’ó ṣàì gbàgbọ́, bákan náà ni fún wọn, yálà o kìlọ̀ fún wọn tàbí o ò kìlọ̀ fún wọn, wọn kò níí gbàgbọ́"
  2,7,Allāhu fi èdídí dí ọkàn wọn àti ìgbọ́rọ̀ wọn. Èbìbò sì bo ìríran wọn. Ìyà ńlá sì wà fún wọn